---
import StoryBand from "./StoryBand.astro";
import onBed from "../images/golden-retriever-on-bed.webp";
---

<StoryBand
    image={onBed}
    imageAlt="Nala resting comfortably on the bed"
    eyebrow="A tiny space wink"
    title="Off exploring (the bed)"
>
    <p>
        Every astronaut needs a place to recharge. Nala's mission control is
        usually whichever cushion is warmest, softest, and most inconvenient to
        disturb.
    </p>
    <p>
        The space theme stays light around here — the real story is just a dog we
        love and a framework I'm enjoying learning.
    </p>
</StoryBand>
